 result‚Üêobject ‚çôConfig arg;setting;value;from;to;dev
‚çù Read and/or write the DeltaWI configuration settings from a list of name-value pairs
‚çù Reading-only names requires an extra level of nesting in order to make it look like shortened name-value pairs

 result‚Üê‚ç¨ ‚çù Return the list of current or previous settings
