 :If 2=‚â¢‚ç¥arg ‚ãÑ arg‚Üê‚Üìarg ‚ãÑ :EndIf ‚çù Allow a one- or two-column matrix instead of a vector of pairs
 :If 2‚â•|‚â°arg ‚ãÑ arg‚Üê,‚äÇarg ‚ãÑ :EndIf ‚çù Force it into a depth-3 vector of name-value pairs
 :For setting :In arg
     :If 1=‚â¢setting‚Üê‚äÜsetting ‚çù They're asking for the current value
         :Select ‚éïC‚äÉsetting
         :Case ‚éïC'Debug' ‚ãÑ result,‚Üê+/object ‚éïVGET‚äÇ'_Debug' 0
